						<summary>

						<p>Much damaged. Seems to refer to a gift of land to the temple of Paraśurāmēśvara of <hi rend="bold">Aṟatuṟēvula</hi> for the merit of <hi rend="bold">Ambadēva-Mahārāja.</hi> Gives also a list of other charities established by the donor whose name is lost.</p>						

						</summary>
